{{Quote|Then if you are done with me, O Great One, I have much work to do. The shipment of tweare skins from Aviprine is due to arrive&mdash;|[[Ogomoor]], to [[Soergg Vosadii Bezhin]]|<ref name="TAS">''[[The Approaching Storm]]''</ref>}}
'''Aviprine''' was an area on [[Ansion/Legends|Ansion]] where [[tweare]]s were raised for their skin.

==Behind the scenes==
[[Jason Fry]], co-author of ''[[The Essential Atlas]]'', confirmed in [[June]] [[2015]] that Aviprine was a location on Ansion.<ref name="Email">{{EmailCite|email=File:EAOC discussion.jpg|creator=Jason Fry|date=2015-06-30}}</ref>

